<br>
Apollo turned into his normal form, dressed in a white tunic with his normal knee length cape, with all the gold trimmings. Noticing the change in energies Artemis looked up at Apollo an approving smile onher face. He raised his hand, as if to say &quot;I'll do what I can&quot;, and vanished.<br>
<br>
The bustling, growing city of Rome. Indeed it would be responcible for the fall of Greece, he and the Fates alone knew this, but he also knew that his greatness would not fade, but grow as Roman's spread the Greco-Roman culture through-out the world. Apollo stood atop a towering building, knelt down looking at jail-house Lysippe was being held in. Apollo jumped from the building, turning into a mouse on the way down, he gently landed on the cill of the bared window to Lysippe's room.<br>
<br>
Hopping down onto her head, the blonde, blue-eyed mouse was quite the spectacle. Apollo squeeked and licked Lysippe's face waiting for her to wake up. He would do all in his power to help  her. <p>     *~*The Golden God*~*
